Version 2.2.1

1.) [hardy] fix sound on resume from suspend LP Bug #223742
    (serp3) (serp4) (gazp5) (gazv5) (panv3)
2.) Install linux-backports-modules-hardy to fix the wireless
    LED on Intel based cards LP Bug #223874

